                            <comment id="14073682" author="jmhsieh" created="Thu, 24 Jul 2014 21:33:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;looks fine.  Is the idea just for specialized benchmarking?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Is there an easy way to get unit tests to exercise this new config?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14090340" author="stack" created="Fri, 8 Aug 2014 05:46:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jmhsieh&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jmhsieh&quot;&gt;Jonathan Hsieh&lt;/a&gt; for review.&lt;/p&gt;

